OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry evening
OL,6,Fwith plenty of evening sunshine with
OL,7,Fclear skies following for many. A band
OL,8,Fof thicker cloud will spread south
OL,9,Finto northern parts after midnight,
OL,10,Fbut likely staying dry. Staying
OL,11,Fclearer further south.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FSunny start for most, with
OL,14,Fsome patchy cloud around, before
OL,15,Fthicker cloud spreads south through
OL,16,Fthe afternoon. Likely dry, but very
OL,17,Fisolated showers possible later. Very
OL,18,Fwarm again, but breezier.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
