OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FCooler
OL,6,Fwith sunny spells and showers Sunday,
OL,7,Fthese perhaps heavy at times. Dry for
OL,8,Fmost Monday, with lighter winds,
OL,9,Fvariable cloud and sunny periods. Warm
OL,10,Fagain Tuesday, with sunny spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
